; Coverage test for history.cc L337, L397, L405, L407
; Tests find_price returning nullopt when:
;   - Source commodity has no adjacent edges (L337: single-target)
;   - Source and target are the same (L397: source == target)
;   - Target has no graph_index (L405/L407: out of range)
;
; Uses -X with a target commodity that has no price relationship
; to the source commodity, exercising the no-path-found return.

P 2024/01/01 GBP $1.30

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    10 EUR
    Assets:Cash     -10 EUR

; EUR has no price to GBP or $, so conversion fails silently
test bal -X GBP
             -10 EUR  Assets:Cash
              10 EUR  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test

; EUR has no price at all, -V finds no price
test bal -V
             -10 EUR  Assets:Cash
              10 EUR  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
